Maintainer: Matthias Gondan <Matthias.Gondan-Rochon@uibk.ac.at>
Description: This R package connects to SWI-Prolog,
        <https://www.swi-prolog.org/>, so that R can send deterministic
        and non-deterministic queries to prolog (consult, query/submit,
        once, findall).
